Description
Product Research
Customer Reviews (33)
Q & A







DeSantis Pocket Shot™ Holster






A unique and effective way to conceal a small semiautomatic pistol. This all-leather holster disguises itself as a wallet, but it can be brought into action instantly without removing the pistol, and it won’t interfere with magazine release or safety operation. Ambidextrous. Made in USA.


   



Text Size:
AAA










